# security: linkpage core publishes ONLY index.html at root.
# Subdirs below are managed manually outside the linkpage flow
# (their contents are still scanned for secret patterns by guard).
*
!index.html
!.gitignore
!note-lp-edu/
!note-lp-edu/**
!note-lp-sales/
!note-lp-sales/**
!note-lp-simple/
!note-lp-simple/**
!vip-download/
!vip-download/**
